Rails3 + Devise + Rspec + Cucumber
========================

You can use this project as a starting point for a Rails web application. It requires Rails 3 and uses Devise http://github.com/plataformatec/devise for user management and authentication, showing how to add RSpec and Cucumber.
________________________

See the README file on GitHub

For more information, please see the updated README file on GitHub:

https://github.com/railsapps/rails3-devise-rspec-cucumber

